Terrier transfer stage\n\n## SAS / RCS\n- SAS / attitude authority via HECS reaction wheel and kRPC autopilot\n- RCS not included\n\n## Operator notes\nBuild identically to attempt 2 / attempt 1. No design changes are intended in this iteration.\n'})
